                <div align="left">
                  <p><img src="/images/acoustic_foam_singapore_specs_3d_foam.jpg" alt="Acoustic Foams" width="100%" height="250" longdesc="/acoustic_foams_singapore.php"><br>
                    <br>
                    <span class="A15ProductContentText"><strong>PRODUCT</strong>:<br>
                    NoiseBlock&trade; Icoustic&trade; 3 Dimentional Acoustic Foam<br>
                    <br>
                    <strong>DESCRIPTION</strong>:<br>
                    <em>NoiseBlock i</em>Coustic&trade; 3D Foam is one of next generation acoustic foams it has a speical configeration different to that of the old acoustic foams seen on the market from the past.<br>
                    The reason behind the name 3D foam is because of the way it scatters and diffuses sound waves that come into contract with it.<br>
                    <br>
                    The reflection angle of the Isosceles Pyramid creates a 3 dimentional reflection point when sound makes contact with the object. This 3 Dimentional reflection is point of the surface does not allow for a the total sum of 100 % of reflection due to the material itself being absorbent to 50%.<br>
                    <br>
                    <strong>COMPOSITION</strong>:<br>
                    Synthetic Multi Polymer, comprising of trace elements of ethylene  propylene diene, isocyanates and polyols. This is then formed into a medium density geometric shape that is in the form of an Isosceles Pyramid. The cell strucutre is loosly formed in clusters whereas other area the cell structure is tight in formation.<br>
                    <br>
                    <strong>APPLICATIONS: </strong><br>
                    3 Dimentional Acoustic Foam can be used for standard entry level enviroments such as studios, music rooms, music pratice rooms, vocal recording booths, home cinemas, schools and much more.<br>
                    <br>
                    It also can be used in conjunction with <a href="/acoustic_panels_diffusers.php" class="2015-ProductContentTextLinks">NoiseBlock Quadratic Panel system</a> for use in home music rooms, theatres, shopping mall ceilings, office spaces, public enviroments, balcony ceilings to name just a few.<br>
                    <br>
                    <strong>CHARACTERISTICS:</strong><br>
&bull; Non Self Adhesive &amp; Self Adhesive<br>
&bull; Non Flame Retardent as standard / can be made in Flame Retardent if required (FR) <br>
&bull; Comes in various different colours / Black, Grey, White, Green, Red, Blue, Purple etc. <br>
&bull; Pyramid Shaped <br>
                    <br>
                    <strong>MODELS / VARIANTS: </strong><br>
                    <br>
                    <strong>&bull; 3D Foam </strong><br>
                    <strong>SIZE:</strong> 500mm x 500mm x 45mm Height (Pyramid: 40mm x 40mm x 40mm) <br>
                    <strong>DENSITY:</strong> 25 KG Density / m&sup3;<br>
                    <strong>NRC:</strong> 0.55<br>
                    <strong>RT:</strong> 2.0ms (After installation onto ceiling within room size of 12 m&sup2;<br>
                    <strong>CAC:</strong> 50 @ 700hz</span></p>
                  <p class="A15ProductContentText"><br>
